OL,10,     FObservatory in California? Find
OL,11,     Fout today.
OL,12,G0710 Abandoned Engineering
OL,13,     FLost Bridges: Hear about some
OL,14,     Fmagnificent bridges that time
OL,15,     Fforgot. A hurricane put paid to
OL,16,     FGoat Canyon Trestle in California,
OL,17,     Fwhile Kinzua Viaduct was destroyed
OL,18,     Fby a tornado.
